1. There were significant differences between treatment groups for parent-reported overall psychosocial health.

6. The p-value for the difference in mental health was 0.001.
7. There were significant differences between treatment groups for behaviour.

9. The differences were in favour of exercising into the hypermobile range.
10. The number of participants in the group exercising into the hypermobile range was 11.
11. The number of participants in the neutral only group was 14.
